The evidence with the title 'Changing the Christmas Tree at the White House ' says Recycled rumor claims the Obamas have replaced the White House christmas tree with a "holiday tree," and without any religious-themed ornaments.  ... 2012 update: the 2012 White House christmas tree, clearly labeled as such, was delivered to Michelle Obama at the North Portico of the White House on nov. 23, 2012. 
